Rating: 4
This was really good. Used the lamb bone from Easter dinner. Took suggestions of other reviewers and did not strain, added more spinach, the beef broth instead of 1/2 the water. Also added garlic and white pepper. The only thing I will do differently next time is to make the broth portion ahead and skim off the fat, before adding back the veggies and meat, and adding spinach and orzo.

